[ext_resource type="Script" path="res://scripts/test_map_01.gd" id="1_map"]

; Rome — UNSEEN, Phase 10. A small STREET-ONLY arena: a dense warren of tight 1-cell
; lanes between Roman insulae blocks, a central fountain piazza, and two small market
; squares. SAME play size as the compact arena (1440x1120) but a denser 19x15 grid for
; cramped, winding streets. NO rooftops, NO sewers, NO portals — just roads (the brief).
; Reuses the WHOLE test_map_01 generator; only the grid, size, feature counts, the
; portal toggle, and the warm Roman palette change. Connectivity flood-fill verified
; (scratchpad/gen_rome.py): 148 open cells, all reachable, spawn corners open.

